items.title: U.S. Natural Gas Futures Fall
items.description: European natural gas prices rose in evening trade as the end of the Russia-Ukraine gas transit deal looms.

items.title: Metal Prices Mixed; Copper and Aluminum End 2024 With Minor Gains
items.description: Metal prices were mixed, with LME three-month copper down 1.6% at $8,790.50 a metric ton and LME three-month aluminum up 0.2% at $2,555.00 a ton.

items.title: U.S. Stocks Rise on Last Day of Stellar Year
items.description: U.S. stocks rose, with tech shares back on top for the final day of 2024.

items.title: Crude Oil Futures Steady
items.description: Oil futures were little changed on the last trading day of 2024, with prices close to where they started the year.

items.title: Why the Dollar's Epic Rally Could Have a Little Further to Run
items.description: The dollar is benefiting from U.S. exceptionalism and entering the new year on a high. Most signs point to more strength ahead.
